Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on mobile-edge computing and device-to-device communication, which are both related to networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper deals with distributed computing at the network edge, which falls under the scope of distributed computing. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper involves optimization of resource allocation and task assignment, which are related to systems and control. 
4. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves optimization of communication and computation resources, which are related to information theory. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Although not the main focus, the paper mentions the use of a heuristic scheme, which is related to machine learning.
